I've got Thaumcraft 4.1.1.14, Baubles 1.0.1.4, and Forge 10.0.1205. I have a world that I generated only with Forge active, and I see what world generation effects different mods have by recreating that world with those mods active and playing with it a bit in single-player.
When I recreate that world with only Forge, Baubles, and Thaumcraft active, the internal server closes after a few laggy seconds of play. Some but not all of the surrounding chunks have been rendered before the server closes.

Here are the crash reports and logs generated:
