https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B5clrhpvkhheU3lobm4tcHBTcW8/edit?usp=sharing

Note that the crash reports complain about an Aspect Orb. So surely the problem does lie with Thaumcraft on this one. I've observed that, as long as Thaumcraft isn't in my mods folder, I don't have this problem or a problem comparable to it when playing with my other mods.

If you want to try to duplicate my experience, the world uses the default world generation, I enter in survival with cheats enabled, and the seed I'm using is:
WHEN YOU WALK AWAY

